{"tid":1180613,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"出到嚟做嘢，點解有人覺得自己因為做得耐做得辛苦而自豪","createTime":"2019-06-01T03:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:33:05.000Z","uid":134474,"like":65,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6268bebebba404096badaded25c2f209edb47bd4","tid":1180613,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:33:30.000Z","msg":"阿仔/阿女，我之前做16，17個鐘，成身攰都未呻，你做得少少嘢都未及我就唔應該叫辛苦，捱埋佢啦<br />\n<br />\n做得辛苦做得耐唔代表你勁，亦唔代表其他人做得少而呻辛苦係冇用<br />\n<br />\n做到成隻狗而唔呻咁呢啲咁羞恥嘅事竟然有人拎嚟自豪打飛機，呢件事係唔應該大肆宣傳<br />\n<br />\n然後再壓制其他人冇資格叫辛苦<br />\n<br />\n奴隸去強迫其他人成為奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c300a00a88b767b57e3ca400ec715dbb4fdc3d","tid":1180613,"uid":24750,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"講緊自己？"},{"pid":"5c0f258dc83933c84e9b3f31cf8142f1b69c9da4","tid":1180613,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"咁真係要揾食嘛"},{"pid":"a1bd4d866bee09ad707e166b2b63d06439dbef85","tid":1180613,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"做十幾個鐘頭係唔應該自豪，係覺得羞恥<br />\n下次係應該向上面企硬，唔係去話其他人唔 捱得"},{"pid":"f14e2c2ce89fb0dfa8f91d094954f69e99df16ee","tid":1180613,"uid":134474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c0f258dc83933c84e9b3f31cf8142f1b69c9da4","tid":1180613,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"咁真係要揾食嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"你搵食你個問題，其他人都要搵食，但唔代表其他人要陪做奴隸，冇資格呻辛苦"},{"pid":"e4441172136644dd63050fbe3709c4aa03a22d37","tid":1180613,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f14e2c2ce89fb0dfa8f91d094954f69e99df16ee","tid":1180613,"uid":134474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c0f258dc83933c84e9b3f31cf8142f1b69c9da4","tid":1180613,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":